snippet: The Israeli military said soldiers opened fire after explosives were thrown at them in the Qalandia refugee camp in the West Bank.
abstract: Israeli military reports special forces shot one Palestinian man and wounded another in Qalandia refugee camp in West Bank when clashes broke out during overnight military operation.
lead_paragraph: The Israeli military said soldiers opened fire after explosives were thrown at them in the Qalandia refugee camp in the West Bank.

headline.main: Israeli Forces Kill Palestinian in Raid of West Bank Camp
headline.print_headline: Israel: Forces Kill Palestinian in Raid
